      "implementation_loop": {
        "description": "Build, test, and iterate — the main development cycle.",
        "entry_criteria": [
          "ARCHITECTURE.md is complete and all spikes in RISK_SPIKES.md are resolved or explicitly deferred with a decision.",
          "TEST_STRATEGY.md is complete with a requirements-to-test traceability matrix covering all P0 requirements.",
          "Every P0 requirement in REQUIREMENTS.md has at least one named purpose test.",
          "DECISION_LOG.md is current — no decisions made since the last stage that are not recorded."
        ],
        "first_steps": [
          "Scaffold the project structure — run the appropriate project initializer (e.g. create-next-app, uv init, cargo init) based on your PRODUCT_SHAPE and ARCHITECTURE.md technology decisions.",
          "Write the first purpose test before writing the first feature. Pick the highest-risk P0 requirement and write its test first so the first line of feature code has something to fail.",
          "Commit after each meaningful unit of work so the drift check has a clean baseline for the next advance.",
          "Run 'programstart status' if you are unsure what to do next — it will surface the active stage and any blockers."
        ],
